  "text": "For evaluation, we use the ClueWeb collection (category B) [CITATION_1] that contains about 50 million documents. We use two query sets: 1-50 from TREC 2009 (ClueWeb-09), and, 51-100 from TREC 2010 (ClueWeb-10).",
